    public class ClientBroker
extends java.lang.Object

      • search

        public java.util.List search(java.lang.String item,
                    java.lang.String type)
        Method to search the Client RandomAccessFile back end allowing a search to be carried out based on the following criteria: membership id, name, or client type.
        Specified by:
        search in interface Broker
        Parameters:
        item - a String containing the value of the item to search for.
        type - a String containing the type of search to be performed. Valid types are: "id", "name", or "type".
        Returns:
        a List of Client objects matching the search criteria that are passed on to the GUI front end. The list is originally created by the back end as an ArrayList and returned as a List.
